gcc14 adds C23 to Slackware

This is a minimal gcc14 with only C language. This adds new C23 specifically to
gcc minimal simple clean build. It might conflict with gcc14 from slackbuilds.org. 

There is no source file but you can simply add

export CC=/opt/gcc14/bin/gcc
export PATH=/opt/gcc14/bin:$PATH"
# this one might be need for the app after you built it
export LD_LIBRARY_PATH="/opt/gcc14/lib64:$LD_LIBRARY_PATH"
